## Content Calendar Management Workflow

- [ ] 1. Set objectives: Align calendar with campaign and business goals
- [ ] 2. Audit existing content: What's already performing well?
- [ ] 3. Define cadence: Set publishing frequency per platform
- [ ] 4. Plan content themes: Map content themes to business objectives
- [ ] 5. Build the calendar: Assign content to specific dates and platforms
- [ ] 6. Include campaigns: Overlay campaign dates and key moments
- [ ] 7. Assign owners: Who is creating, reviewing, and publishing each piece?
- [ ] 8. Review and adjust: Weekly review to ensure on-track delivery

## Key Inputs
- Brand: {{brand_name}}
- Platforms: {{platforms}}
- Publishing cadence: {{publishing_cadence}}
- Campaigns: {{campaigns}}
- Content themes: {{content_themes}}
